  <brief_title>A Phase 1 Study of Brentuximab Vedotin Combined With Multi-Agent Chemotherapy for Hodgkin Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1 Dose-Escalation Safety Study of Brentuximab Vedotin in Combination With Multi-Agent Chemotherapy as Frontline Therapy in Patients With Hodgkin Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
